<!--***********************************************************
*  Example 5:  Using the "sectionWideCheckWork" attribute 
*  and "aggregateScores" attribute within a subsection --
*  Method 2: Using a boolean statement nested within an 
*  the <answer></answer> and following the list of choices.
*  The boolean syntax is: 
*  <award><when>conditional statement</when></award>
************************************************************-->



<section><p><em>Robot/AI trivia game Part 2</em></p>

<p>The "sectionWideCheckWork" and "aggregateScores" attributes can be used within a <tag>subsection</tag><tag>/subsection</tag> to suppress solution checking on individual problems.  This atttribute allows for one single checkwork button to occur at the bottom of the subsection.</p>
  
<p>In this example, the "correct" choice is marked by a boolean within the <tag>answer</tag><tag>/answer</tag> component below the choice definitions.</p>

  
  <subsection sectionWideCheckWork aggregateScores>
  <ol> 
    <li>Who is the famous AI/humanoid robot in Star Trek?
        <choiceinput name="answer1">
          <choice>Sonny</choice>
          <choice>Data</choice>
          <choice>Hal</choice>
        </choiceinput>
      <answer>
        <award>
          <when>$answer1=<text>Hal</text>
          </when>
        </award>
      </answer>
    </li>
    <li>What animated robot was originally designed by his creator to be a personal healthcare companion?
        <choiceinput name="answer2">
          <choice>the Iron Giant</choice>
          <choice>Baymax</choice>
          <choice>Bender</choice>
        </choiceinput>
      <answer>
        <award>
          <when>$answer2=Baymax
          </when>
        </award>
      </answer>
    </li>
    <li>Which robot is a character of the dystopian 1985 film Brazil?
        <choiceinput name="answer3">
          <choice>Machinemens</choice>
          <choice>RoboCop</choice>
          <choice>the Terminator</choice>
        </choiceinput>
      <answer>
        <award>
          <when>$answer3=Machinemensch
          </when>
        </award>
      </answer>
    </li>
  </ol>
  </subsection>
</section>


